node.text: Today we're sharing what might be one of the most fun webisodes yet: our very own Syd gave us a tour of the McGee's pool and pool house, so you'll definitely want to tune in to hear his thoughts. Spoiler alert: he ends up in the water fully clothed 😆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Studio McGee on July 20, 2021 tagging @nicole_franzen, and @leannefordinteriors. May be an image of furniture, brick wall and living room.

node.text:
For today's Make Life Beautiful feature we're learning more about the lovely @leannefordinteriors. She's the star of Home Again with the Fords on HGTV, designer behind many of our favorite rooms, and someone who reminds us that there's so much beauty to be found in home — wherever that may be. Hear her interview on the blog today!

Photo by @nicole_franzen for @dominomag

node.text: We’re so excited to share that our sweet baby girl is here! Margot McGee joined our family Sunday morning and we’re over the moon soaking up every bit of her newborn goodness. 💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Studio McGee on July 19, 2021. May be an image of flower, tree and pool.

node.text: Our girls’ favorite activity this summer was taking care of their very pregnant mother with a game they called “resort.” They’d put on aprons and bring her endless Diet Cokes. It might be one of the best parts about hanging out by the pool! 💦 — Syd

node.text: If you've been following along for a while you know how excited the family is that our pool is finally finished! We worked with @nauticapoolsutah and @decorativelandscaping to fulfill this lifelong dream of ours, and we can't wait to enjoy it for years to come. Make your way to the blog to get details on the materials, surroundings, and more! 📷: @lucycall
